<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA12">
<l>atuvē pirāṉāmā ṟāṭkoḷḷu māṟu</l>
<l>matuvē yiṉiyaṟintō māṉā - latuvē</l>
<l>paṉikkaṇaṅku kaṇṇiyā roṇṇutaliṉ mēlōr</l>
<l>taṉikkaṇaṅku vaittār takavu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That is the way the lord is and the way he makes servants.</l>
<l>That we have understood now. That</l>
<l>is befitting for him with a chaplet tormented by the dew, him who put</l>
<l>there a solitary eye on [his] bright forehead.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
